Package org.apache.nemo.common.ir

Interface OutputCollector<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - output type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataFetcherOutputCollector, GBKTransform.GBKOutputCollector, OperatorVertexOutputCollector, OperatorWatermarkCollector, RunTimeMessageOutputCollector
    public interface OutputCollector<O>
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface through which Transform emits outputs. This is to be implemented in the runtime with runtime-specific distributed data movement and storage mechanisms.
